English:
Our leader mostly keeps to himself. To be honest,
I can count the times we've met on one hand.
Chinese:
我們的隊長不太會出現在眾人面前。
我也只見過他一兩次而已……
Korean:
우리들의 리더는 남들 앞에 그다지 모습을 드러내지 않아.
우리들도 한두 번밖에 보지 못했는걸…
German:
Unser Anführer bleibt meistens alleine. Ich kann
an einer Hand abzählen, wie oft ich ihn getroffen
habe.

English: I wonder what he's always off doing...
Chinese: 隊長他平時都在做些什麼事呢？
German:
Was er wohl immer macht, wenn er alleine unterwegs
ist ...?

English: If you've something to ask, out with it.
Chinese: 你不是有事情想要問我嗎？
German: Wenn du was fragen willst, dann spuck’s aus.
